We could scale using:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
\Omega_{\alpha c} & =\frac{N_{\alpha}g^{2}}{\sqrt{\Delta^{2}+\frac{\kappa^{2}}{4}}}.
\end{align}

\end_inset


